<section class="why-section">
<div class="container">
	<div class="section-label">// details</div>
	<div class="features-grid">
		<div class="feature">
			<div class="feature-title">No dependencies</div>
			<div class="feature-desc">Core parser and BM25 router ship zero external deps. Just Node.</div>
		</div>
		<div class="feature">
			<div class="feature-title">Vendor neutral</div>
			<div class="feature-desc">Not tied to any specific model or platform. Works with any agent framework.</div>
		</div>
		<div class="feature">
			<div class="feature-title">8 lint rules</div>
			<div class="feature-desc">Catches hardcoded paths, secrets in prompts, missing error handling, weak descriptions.</div>
		</div>
		<div class="feature">
			<div class="feature-title">Quality scoring</div>
			<div class="feature-desc">0–100 across 5 dimensions. Plug it into CI and fail builds below a threshold.</div>
		</div>
		<div class="feature">
			<div class="feature-title">BM25 routing</div>
			<div class="feature-desc">Full-text search. Picks the right skill from 10k+ in milliseconds. No API keys.</div>
		</div>
		<div class="feature">
			<div class="feature-title">OpenAPI → SKILL.md</div>
			<div class="feature-desc">Feed it an OpenAPI 3.x spec, get back valid SKILL.md files. That's it.</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
</section>

<style>
	.why-section { padding: 0; }

	.features-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 1.25rem;
	}

	.feature {
		padding: 1rem;
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: 8px;
	}

	.feature-title {
		font-size: 0.78rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
	}

	.feature-desc {
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		color: var(--muted);
		line-height: 1.5;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.features-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
	}
</style>
